Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:09.12,BT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\pos(114,68)}{\fad(1500,0)}晓\N之\N蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可真是悠闲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.79,0:02:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 要每天总这么暖洋洋的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人就渐渐变懒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.11,0:02:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近我老婆吊儿郎当地睡过了头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.07,0:02:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连早饭都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春眠不觉晓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且最近突然忘事忘得厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前一段竟把孩子忘在集市里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.95,0:02:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真过分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.95,0:02:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去以后没把你的脸忘记就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那反而要庆幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.83,0:03:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妻子 没有晚上睡不着的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.09,0:03:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡觉时酣声很大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.24,0:03:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.22,0:03:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵得我睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治打酣的药倒是有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.97,0:03:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那东西有没有用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 你们刚才说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.55,0:03:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治打酣的药吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.89,0:03:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是忘事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上睡不着 是有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么想法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.61,0:03:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快救救我 楫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:03:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有只奇怪的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.28,0:04:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说螃蟹吗 连这个都忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年这季节都会从河上爬上来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.80,0:04:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是楫的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 今天是初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是虫师银古
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以打搅一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不用客气 我是楫的母亲小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本总是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来嘛 可以说是稳重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,0:04:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也经常忘事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.98,0:04:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大概从去年春天开始 忘事忘得蹊跷起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 很少见的来了很多客人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我买了娘很喜欢吃的糯米丸子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点心真好吃 娘还是第一次吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么啊 不是偶尔也吃吃的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.15,0:05:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事 你是说我瞒着你偷吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.74,0:05:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娘失去了跟糯米丸子有关的全部记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而另外一天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怎么穿的打算卖掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有这种衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因为很贵 所以小心保管的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这种衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因为衬托得脸色不好看不穿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.21,0:05:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连不怎么穿的和服 也会只忘记有花纹的那些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真冷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吓我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要突然做奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.83,0:06:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是个喷嚏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.34,0:06:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喷嚏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连喷嚏都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正月去亲戚家的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楫 对面那两个人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.31,0:06:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正叔和实婶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.56,0:06:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那旁边的是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连妹妹都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说是忘事还不如说是进行性记忆丧失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不分昼夜总起来活动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前明明做家务时抽空也要在那棵树下睡午觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对有什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭做好了 银古也请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.76,0:07:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没什么好招待的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.52,0:07:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下把你娘忘了的事 尽可能想起来然后写出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.03,0:07:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别介意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是给外出旅行的丈夫的阴膳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(432,20)}{\fs18\shad0\fnsimhei\1c&HFFFFFF}阴膳:为祈祷外出旅行的人平安而在家里供的饭。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.48,0:07:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阴膳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是一年到头到处跑的旅行商人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说这样一来就不用为旅途中的饭食发愁了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是为了让自己安心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会是连丈夫死了都忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太浪费了 算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没多少
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:07:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份是从娘的口粮里扣出来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为爹是为了谁在旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可比留在家里的娘肚子饿得多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为干这个根本赚不了多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在附近工作不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.07,0:08:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常早到该回来的时候了 现在连封信都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为娘总这么糊涂 一直让爹担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.95,0:08:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.33,0:08:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了就走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 那孩子也只是希望父亲在身边而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.66,0:08:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我丈夫也…很温柔 人很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是在哪里迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.98,0:08:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他担心的 似乎不只是父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是受那孩子所托而来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我听了大致的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 你知道些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还什么也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.80,0:09:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.05,0:09:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然也为了我自己 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样下去的话总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会连丈夫和那孩子都忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 连忘记这件事本身都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.74,0:09:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 比什么都可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.24,0:09:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,列好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.14,0:09:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 基本列好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为忘的事里可能有一定的规律
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是靠这些看不出倾向
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 忘掉的亲戚里有什么共同点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是住在河对岸的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去集市也见不到的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单纯只是相遇的次数少而忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.93,0:10:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 要那样的话早该把丈夫忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天都快亮了 完全没睡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.35,0:10:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使想睡也睡不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:11:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以半夜就那样一边织布
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边为了不忘记爹而反复想他的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.32,0:11:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少能睡的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待也能轻松点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖风
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.44,0:11:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织布机的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.09,0:11:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样夜里做事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了落入深深的睡眠深渊里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.17,0:11:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于开始有睡意了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 已经早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做饭做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃记忆的虫?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 叫影魂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们呈半透明的黑色幕状
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.44,0:12:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢老的大树的影子 与其同化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里等待休息的人和动物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦开始进入睡眠它们就从耳朵进入其脑中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:13:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来寄主就基本不再睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点点丧失记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.34,0:13:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在院子里那棵樱树的影子里有那个?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且吃了一定量的记忆后在内部分裂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在寄主仅有的一点睡眠时间里将分身放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.47,0:13:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放出来的再潜入树影里 它们就靠此增多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们本来是长时间被日光照就会消失的弱小生物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一旦让它们潜入体内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.86,0:13:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会深入脑中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从而无法对它们出手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.68,0:13:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说无法治愈了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据我所知影魂的弱点 只有日光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.10,0:13:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那无法照到脑里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.63,0:13:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是可能能守住不想忘记的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说 记忆就像是被收拾到橱柜里的东西一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.08,0:14:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“糯米丸子”“住在远处的亲戚”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“喷嚏”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些东西被分装在无数个抽屉里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影魂把那些东西从一个个抽屉里拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那顺序与你的关心无关
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来完全没有秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.11,0:14:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 只有一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有不会被影魂入侵的一部分记忆群
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是每天反复做 看 想的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.82,0:14:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做饭的方法 织布的方法 儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在记忆中相见的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.31,0:14:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能影魂为了不让寄主死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:15:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而将日常生活基本所需要做的事的记忆留了下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说那些事不会忘掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.87,0:15:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底还是推测
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.11,0:15:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 如果将来你的记忆被吃到底的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候那些事可能也会被吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我能说的对策就是储存更多的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.26,0:15:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管多少次都要把不想忘的事想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 就这么试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.79,0:15:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 娘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.36,0:15:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别一直呆在家里 出去走走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 就这么做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找你没回来的爹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.56,0:15:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.54,0:15:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦 那么惊诧的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:16:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是又怕知道你爹出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我 已经等够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.41,0:16:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但怎么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爹总说西街的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.19,0:16:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先从那里找起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会跟我一起去吧 楫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.85,0:16:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就到这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们才是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.04,0:16:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个决断 对两人来说是好是坏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.83,0:16:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我知道原委正好过了一年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呦 回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银古
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.44,0:17:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.16,0:17:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 看起来精神不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到你爹了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在西街
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里和别的家人一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到前面那家去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.09,0:17:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娘 为什么什么也不说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:17:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.29,0:18:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回途中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.01,0:18:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娘只是默默地走个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,0:18:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不食不休 终于
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娘 娘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能由于太过劳累
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娘病倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那样睡了好几天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.27,0:19:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才 有什么东西出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 那副表情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 睡得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 做饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们为什么会在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去山里玩 正在回家路上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.06,0:20:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.18,0:20:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.22,0:20:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃点东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 肚子都饿得扁扁的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.39,0:20:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.05,0:20:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天早上 娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我 家 还有身边的几样事之外
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.79,0:20:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丧失了全部的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她昏睡的时候 大半记忆都被吞噬了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是 没忘记做饭的方法和我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们按银古说的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天出去遇到各种各样的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.23,0:21:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些也基本都在第二天忘光了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.93,0:21:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但似乎每天都很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还是基本不睡觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 晚上还是不停织布
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.70,0:21:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 还是没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是没变
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.17,0:21:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭快好了 去洗手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.29,0:22:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娘 又多了一份
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.41,0:22:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 明明只做我和你的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底为什么觉得非这么做不可
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.69,0:22:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不知怎的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.75,0:22:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就觉得安心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.13,0:22:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.45,0:23:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取空茧
